<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 08:09:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡与正统派的不正当联盟是他的又一失败之举</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-crooked-alliance-with-the-haredim-is-another-feather-of-failure-in-his-cap/0000018e-7cd8-d9f5-a7ae-7edd2ae00000</link><description>以色列总理对军队征召极端正统派人士的法律处理不当，包括拖延、投降和对形势的错误解读。照常。然而，这一次，他的犯罪同伙将首先受苦</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 04:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-crooked-alliance-with-the-haredim-is-another-feather-of-failure-in-his-cap/0000018e-7cd8-d9f5-a7ae-7edd2ae00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对唯一关心以色列利益的世界强国的令人困惑的蔑视</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-confounding-contempt-for-the-only-world-power-with-israels-interest-at-heart/0000018e-7c90-d680-a1cf-fe97200e0000</link><description>以色列完全依赖美国，但总理 — — 没有美国的批准，他什么也做不了 — — 却喋喋不休地谈论“全面胜利”。此外，美国对以色列的任何额外制裁都会对北方可能发生的战争产生影响</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 04:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-confounding-contempt-for-the-only-world-power-with-israels-interest-at-heart/0000018e-7c90-d680-a1cf-fe97200e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军袭击黎巴嫩后，一名男子在以色列北部发射的重型火箭弹中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article-live/israeli-hostage-uriel-baruch-was-killed-on-oct-7-body-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-family-says/0000018e-7dc0-d680-a1cf-ffc7736c0000</link><description>西岸巴勒斯坦当局报告 3 人在以色列国防军杰宁行动中丧生 ■ 家人称，人质尤里尔·巴鲁克 (Uriel Baruch) 于 10 月 7 日被杀，尸体被哈马斯在加沙扣押 ■ 纽约时报：前以色列人质遭到性侵犯和酷刑 ■ 美国称以色列声称联合国决议弃权阻碍人质协议谈判“不准确”</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 02:37:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article-live/israeli-hostage-uriel-baruch-was-killed-on-oct-7-body-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-family-says/0000018e-7dc0-d680-a1cf-ffc7736c0000</guid></item><item><title>长期担任 AIPAC 主席的霍华德·科尔将于 2024 年底辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/howard-kohr-longtime-aipac-chief-to-step-down-at-the-end-of-2024/0000018e-7cc8-d3d0-a7af-fecaf01c0000</link><description>该公告发布之际，AIPAC 在 2024 年选举周期中的作用和信息传递受到越来越多的审查，特别是在哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击和随后的加沙战争之后</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 22:13:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/howard-kohr-longtime-aipac-chief-to-step-down-at-the-end-of-2024/0000018e-7cc8-d3d0-a7af-fecaf01c0000</guid></item><item><title>美国反驳内塔尼亚胡关于联合国投票损害停火协议的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/u-s-rejects-netanyahus-suggestion-that-hamas-rejected-truce-deal-because-of-un-vote/0000018e-7c90-d8a5-addf-7cb328250000</link><description>美国国务院称以色列总理的言论“对人质及其家人不公平”，部分原因是哈马斯在联合国安理会投票前准备了回应</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 22:01:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/u-s-rejects-netanyahus-suggestion-that-hamas-rejected-truce-deal-because-of-un-vote/0000018e-7c90-d8a5-addf-7cb328250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质乌里尔·巴鲁克 (Uriel Baruch) 家人称，他被认为被绑架，但已于 10 月 7 日被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/hostage-uriel-baruch-was-killed-on-oct-7-body-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-family-says/0000018e-7ca1-d9f5-a7ae-7eade0880000</link><description>35岁的巴鲁克在诺瓦音乐节上被绑架。他留下了妻子 Racheli、两个分别为 8 岁和 5 岁的孩子、父母和三个兄弟。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 21:30:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/hostage-uriel-baruch-was-killed-on-oct-7-body-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-family-says/0000018e-7ca1-d9f5-a7ae-7eade0880000</guid></item><item><title>美国试图澄清以色列遵守拜登国际法要求的情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/u-s-attempts-to-clarify-status-of-israels-compliance-with-bidens-demands-on-intl-law/0000018e-7c68-d8a5-addf-7cfbd6f90000</link><description>在美国周一表示尚未发现以色列违反国际法后，美国国务院澄清说，尚未就以色列在加沙使用美国提供的武器时是否遵守美国或国际法做出“最终决定”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 20:50:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/u-s-attempts-to-clarify-status-of-israels-compliance-with-bidens-demands-on-intl-law/0000018e-7c68-d8a5-addf-7cfbd6f90000</guid></item><item><title>品牌形象，但色彩不佳：为什么特朗普将哈马斯袭击归咎于以色列，却忽视了人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-26/ty-article/.highlight/on-brand-off-color-why-trump-blames-israel-for-the-hamas-attack-and-ignores-the-hostages/0000018e-7b8d-d680-a1cf-ff8f94fe0000</link><description>特朗普甚至没有承认人质的身份，因为他们的家人越来越公开地依赖拜登政府来达成协议，同时对内塔尼亚胡未能优先释放他们表示遗憾</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 19:26:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-26/ty-article/.highlight/on-brand-off-color-why-trump-blames-israel-for-the-hamas-attack-and-ignores-the-hostages/0000018e-7b8d-d680-a1cf-ff8f94fe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对黎巴嫩发动自战争爆发以来最深入的打击；火箭弹向以色列国防军基地发射</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-strikes-northern-lebanon-rockets-fired-towards-idf-base/0000018e-7bc8-d8a5-addf-7bfb90340000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布袭击了黎巴嫩北部真主党空军的一个军事设施，以回应真主党对梅龙山以色列国防军基地的袭击，这是战争爆发以来的第四次袭击</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 18:24:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-strikes-northern-lebanon-rockets-fired-towards-idf-base/0000018e-7bc8-d8a5-addf-7bfb90340000</guid></item><item><title>获释的以色列人质向《纽约时报》讲述了哈马斯被囚禁期间的性虐待经历</title><link>h