rs-due-to-war-in-north/0000018e-7b8a-d8a5-addf-7bbba3460000</link><description>Coffee Anan 是一家位于戈兰高地风景秀丽的本塔尔山的咖啡馆，在以色列国防军宣布以色列北部大部分地区为军事禁区后，该咖啡馆宣布关闭。咖啡馆的名字是前联合国秘书长科菲·安南和希伯来语“云”一词的组合</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:38:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/popular-golan-heights-cafe-permanently-closes-doors-due-to-war-in-north/0000018e-7b8a-d8a5-addf-7bbba3460000</guid></item><item><title>数十名以色列军事指挥官警告该法案草案将损害国家安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-israeli-military-commanders-warn-draft-bill-would-damage-national-security/0000018e-7b7e-d9f5-a7ae-7f7f972d0000</link><description>在向该国领导人发出的请求中，指挥官们警告不要大幅增加预备役军人服役，同时免除极端正统派人士的计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:31:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-israeli-military-commanders-warn-draft-bill-would-damage-national-security/0000018e-7b7e-d9f5-a7ae-7f7f972d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列令人不安地否认加沙遭受饥饿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/inside-israels-disturbing-denial-of-starvation-in-gaza/0000018e-7b41-d680-a1cf-ff47b4220000</link><description>以色列当局和亲以色列的键盘侠系统地否认专家研究、援助机构和加沙人自己关于加沙灾难性饥饿的证据，他们有明确的、无耻的动机</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:12:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/inside-israels-disturbing-denial-of-starvation-in-gaza/0000018e-7b41-d680-a1cf-ff47b4220000</guid></item><item><title>莫斯科袭击事件后，俄罗斯新的影响力运动试图用草率的希伯来语将责任归咎于西方</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/after-moscow-attack-new-russian-campaign-tries-to-pin-blame-on-west-in-sloppy-hebrew/0000018e-7b63-d96c-af9f-7fe353570000</link><description>莫斯科袭击事件导致至少 139 人死亡，之后以色列社交媒体上出现了数千个账户，并将责任归咎于乌克兰和西方国家。在寻求以色列对恐怖袭击受害者的同情时，该活动的草率希伯来语导致了嘲笑和失败</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/after-moscow-attack-new-russian-campaign-tries-to-pin-blame-on-west-in-sloppy-hebrew/0000018e-7b63-d96c-af9f-7fe353570000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦权利组织在耶路撒冷普珥节街头派对上散发传单，抗议以色列在加沙的行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/group-drops-leaflets-on-purim-street-party-in-jerusalem-protesting-israeli-action-in-gaza/0000018e-7b63-d946-a3ff-7fe7e8980000</link><description>在该组织的 X 帐户上发布的一段视频中，传单在空中漂浮，然后落在普珥节聚会参与者的脚下。传单上用希伯来语写道：“自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列军队已造成 32,000 人死亡。” “超过一百万人处于危险之中。停止屠杀”</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 16:01:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/group-drops-leaflets-on-purim-street-party-in-jerusalem-protesting-israeli-action-in-gaza/0000018e-7b63-d946-a3ff-7fe7e8980000</guid></item><item><title>1300万美元现金从哥伦比亚购买一架私人飞机：对以色列国防出口主管来说不是问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/13m-cash-on-a-private-jet-from-colombia-a-nonissue-for-israeli-head-of-defense-export/0000018e-7689-d706-a39f-f7f93fa10000</link><description>国防部出口援助部门负责人亚伊尔·库拉斯参与了令人惊讶的交易。但本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的新政府拯救了他</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 14:51:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/13m-cash-on-a-private-jet-from-colombia-a-nonissue-for-israeli-head-of-defense-export/0000018e-7689-d706-a39f-f7f93fa10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列不是攻击拉法，而是内塔尼亚胡攻击华盛顿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-israel-attacking-rafah-netanyahu-attacks-washington/0000018e-79e1-d96c-af9f-7fe1f12d0000</link><description>总理本可以通过多种方式表达对联合国安理会决议的不满，但他选择了最糟糕的一种：发动外交攻击，为哈马斯辛瓦尔和真主党服务，并损害将人质带回家的努力</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 12:56:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-israel-attacking-rafah-netanyahu-attacks-washington/0000018e-79e1-d96c-af9f-7fe1f12d0000</guid></item><item><title>由于极端正统政治压力，以色列政府推迟了关于军队豁免法案的会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/govt-vote-on-army-exemption-bill-postponed-following-ultra-orthodox-political-pressure/0000018e-79a0-d680-a1cf-ffa7154f0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理在拒绝支持新版本法案后会见了极端正统党派领导人。会议结束后，提案可能会再次改变</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 12:19:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/govt-vote-on-army-exemption-bill-postponed-following-ultra-orthodox-political-pressure/0000018e-79a0-d680-a1cf-ffa7154f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>